release.notes: Fixed some security hole and changed base language from Japanese to English on the pc_frontend.
Added an ability to render iframes of the outer OpenSocial container and fixed the PersistentAPI.
This version is compatible with Doctrine.
The preseted profile item was made to correspond to API
Fixed MemberApplicationSetting model, because index key is too long.
Added an ability for Albums API.
Added an ability to approve install of the app from SNS admin.
Fixed error when app was searched.
fixed JSON-RPC API because friend data can't be fetched.

Fixed the following bugs. #1823: [pc] UserPref.required is not driving #1825: [etc] Warning in ApplicationUserSettingForm::save() while saving data type of "BOOL" #2046: [pc] "home" view doesn't exists #2047: [pc] opShindigRemoteContentFetcher doesn't send header correctly set #2048: [api] PHP Notice in "lib_for_shindig/OpenPNEService.php" #2049: [pc] Fix a mistake of the relayUrl in gadget component #2050: [api] PersistentAPI doesn't return all key-value pair #2051: [pc] gadgets.container._parseIframeUrl doesn't return first parameter correctly.

Fixed the following bugs. #2100: [api] opOpenSocialProfileExport doesn't return birthday when public flag of birthday is '3' and owner is viewer #2125: [api] /mediaitems/@me/@self/{albumId} で取得できるコレクションの albumId フィールドの値が間違っている #2148: [api] /albums/@me/@self で取得したアルバムのサムネイルが未設定の場合 thumbnailUrl フィールドに間違った値が入る #2212: [etc] NOTICE ファイルの更新 #2217: [pc] Fix two js errors in application/list screen when the user doesn't have any application
Fixed the following issue. #2218: [pc] modalboxを2回目以降に表示すると、読み込みが完了するまで前回表示時の内容が残ってしまう (0.9.x)
Fixed the following bug. #2352: [etc] 部分一致検索を行う箇所でワイルドカード検索ができてしまう
